{"serial": "33069", "department_serial": 31, "code": "ME5209", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Artificial Intelligence and Design Thinking", "ch": "人工智慧與設計思考"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Tsai, Shyi-Jeng", "Chen,Hsiang-Chieh", "Chih-Yang Lin", "Lin, Yuan-Ting", "Liao, Chao-Yaug", "Lin, Chin-Te", "Lee, Ju-Yi"], "ch": ["蔡錫錚", "陳翔傑", "林智揚", "林苑婷", "廖昭仰", "林錦德", "李朱育"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 6, "session": ["1", "2", "3"]}, "loc": {"building": "*", "room": "***"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 30, "department": {"ch": "機械工程學系", "en": "Department of Mechanical Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 29, "selected": 27, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "請務必出席第一堂課：9/10(二)10:00~12:00於E2-452\n實際上課的⽇期與時間：10/5(六)、10/13(日)、10/26(六)、11/10(日)、11/30(六)、12/21(六)。\n在這門的課程中，學生將探討人工智慧（AI）和設計思考（Design Thinking）兩個領域的結合。課程的目的是培養學生創新和解決問題的能力，尤其是在高度AI化和自動化的現代環境下。\n\n主要目標：\n1. 學習基礎的人工智慧概念，包括機器學習、自然語言處理、和電腦視覺。\n2. 掌握設計思考技巧：包含定義問題、創意激發、原型製作、和測試。\n3. 學習如何將人工智慧和設計思考結合，以創造更有效、更人性化的解決方案。", "en": "In this interdisciplinary course, students will explore the intersection of Artificial Intelligence (AI) and Design Thinking. The aim is to equip students with the ability to innovate and problem-solve, particularly in a highly digitized and automated modern context.\n\nPrimary Objectives:\n1. Learn fundamental concepts of AI including machine learning, natural language processing, and computer vision.\n2. Master the stages of Design Thinking: Problem Definition, Ideation, Prototyping, and Testing.\n3. Learn how to combine AI and Design Thinking to create more effective, human-centered solutions."}, "outline": {"ch": "課程內容：\n1. 導論：人工智慧與設計思考導論\n2. 機器學習概念與工具\n2.1 人工智慧概論\n2.2 電腦視覺\n2.3 設計思考基礎\n3. 設計思考\n3.1 問題定義\n3.2 創意方法和工具\n4.  結合的實踐：人工智慧驅動的設計思考\n4.1 如何使用AI生成更多解決方案？\n4.2 如何使用設計思考來指導AI模型的發展？\n5 專案實作和實例研究\n5.1 團隊項目，將人工智慧與設計思考應用到現實問題上\n5.2 展示和評價\n5.3 未來展望", "en": "Course Content:\n1. Introduction: Intersection of AI and Design Thinking\n2. Concepts and tools of machine learning\n2.1 Introduction of AI\n2.2 Computer vision\n2.3 Basics of Design Thinking\n3. Design Thinking\n3.1 Problem definition\n3.2 Creative methods and tools\n4 Integrated Practice: AI-Driven Design Thinking\n4.1 How can AI be used to generate more solutions?\n4.2 How can Design Thinking guide the development of AI models?\n5 Project Work and Case Studies\n5.1 Team projects applying AI and Design Thinking to real-world problems\n5.2 Student presentations and evaluations\n5.3 Potential future developments of AI and Design Thinking"}, "textbook": {"ch": "老師自備", "en": "Provided by Professor"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "50", "en": "50"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "平時成績（參與度、小測驗）：30％\n團隊項目：40％\n期末報告或展示：30％", "en": "Class Participation and Quizzes: 30％\nGroup Project: 40％\nFinal Report or Presentation: 30％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "星期一下午", "en": "Monday afternoon"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "課程活動在週末與合作夥伴協調進行，總時間滿足課程時數的要求。", "en": "The course activities are on weekend days coordinated with the partner, and the period covers the requirements of course hours."}, "domain": {"ch": "設計與分析", "en": "設計與分析"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "專業知識與技能", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "實驗規劃與資料分析", "rating": "(3)普通", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考"]}, {"competencies": "工程設計與整合", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["實作/實驗"]}, {"competencies": "合作溝通與管理", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}, {"competencies": "專業倫理與社會責任", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Engineering Knowledge and Problem Analysis", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": ["Test/Exam"]}, {"competencies": "Experiment and Implementation", "rating": "(3)Medium", "assesments": 